This Rock-A-Palzooza was extra special because @selkirk.shores hosted us at their cozy Airbnb!

We cooked, played games, walked by the lake and enjoyed the hot tub! 

We’ll never forget this experience, thank you @selkirk.shores for helping us make some beautiful memories🥰

Life really is better at the lake!

Double tap if you can relate!

🥳Happy New Year everyone!

I took some time off to enjoy the holidays with my family. I got a lot of 😴sleep and wasn’t very productive.

Today the kids return to school and I’m looking forward to getting back to my regular routine.

Every year my husband and I write down our goals and review them at the end of the year. For 2023, we decided to make a list📝 of the habits🧘🏽‍♀️🥗💪😴we’d like to work on.

Do you like to make new year resolutions, set goals and/or create a vision board? Or do you prefer to just go with the flow?

#Dailygratitude #gratitudequotes #gratitudepractice #lifeonpurpose #changeyourmindset #changeyourlife #mindsetchange #positivemindset #getoutofyourownway #getuncomfortable #doitanyway #juststart #reachyourgoals #nevergiveuponyourdreams #motivateyourself #achieveyourgoals #mindsetmatters #mindsetshift #lifepurpose #souljourney #trustyourpath #youarepowerful #manifestyourlife #soulpurpose #momlifebelike #sahmlife #organizer #minimalisthome #indianmomblogger #indianmommyblogger

What do I want to continue doing?

1. Daily movement and exercise
2. Reducing sugar and eating whole foods
3. Daily exposure to nature, daylight, extreme heat and cold
4. Meditation, journaling and relaxation
5. Improving my sleep 😴 

How will I do it?

1. Staying organized and scheduling my priorities
2. Meal planning and prepping
3. Saying NO to the things that don’t align with these habits
4. Waking up and going to sleep early

Here’s to a healthier lap around the sun☀️
